---
// Challenges Section
// ------------
import Section from '../../ui/Section.astro'
import Row from '../../ui/Row.astro'
import Col from '../../ui/Col.astro'
---

<Section id="challenges" classes="bg-neutral-100 py-16 lg:py-28 dark:bg-neutral-950">
	<Row classes="items-start gap-y-10">
		<Col span="4">
			<p class="mb-4 font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-neutral-500">
				Grid Pressure
			</p>
			<h2 class="max-w-sm font-headings text-3xl font-bold leading-tight text-primary-600 lg:text-4xl">
				Speed to grid is more critical than ever
			</h2>
		</Col>
		<Col span="6" classes="lg:col-start-7">
			<div class="max-w-2xl">
				<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
					As energy demand accelerates, the primary bottleneck has shifted from capital to grid
					capacity. Project viability now depends on the ability to secure and optimize connection
					points before competitors do.
				</p>
				<p class="mt-8 leading-relaxed text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
					Grid constraints are no longer just a technical hurdle. They define market risk across
					BESS, renewable energy projects, and data centres. Revolt provides the strategic clarity
					needed to navigate complex regulatory processes and technical limitations earlier.
				</p>

				<div class="mt-8 border-t border-primary-200 pt-8 dark:border-primary-800/70">
					<div class="grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2">
						<div>
							<p class="mb-1 font-headings text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-primary-600">
								400+
							</p>
							<p class="font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-primary-500">
								Grid scenarios mapped
							</p>
						</div>
						<div>
							<p class="mb-1 font-headings text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-primary-600">
								15ms
							</p>
							<p class="font-mono text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-primary-500">
								Decision latency
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</Col>
	</Row>
</Section>
